module bsg_encode_one_hot (
	i,
	addr_o,
	v_o
);
	parameter width_p = 8;
	parameter lo_to_hi_p = 1;
	input [width_p - 1:0] i;
	output [(width_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p)) - 1:0] addr_o;
	output v_o;
	localparam half_width_lp = width_p >> 1;
	localparam aligned_width_lp = 1 << $clog2(width_p);
	wire [(width_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p)) - 1:0] addr_lo;
	generate
		if (width_p == 1) begin : base
			assign v_o = i;
			assign addr_lo = 1'bX;
		end
		else if (width_p != aligned_width_lp) begin : unaligned
			wire [$clog2(1 << $clog2(width_p)) - 1:0] aligned_addr;
			wire [(aligned_width_lp - width_p) - 1:0] zero_pad = {aligned_width_lp - width_p {1'b0}};
			wire [aligned_width_lp - 1:0] padded = (lo_to_hi_p ? {zero_pad, i} : {i, zero_pad});
			bsg_encode_one_hot #(.width_p(aligned_width_lp)) align(
				.i(padded),
				.addr_o(aligned_addr),
				.v_o(v_o)
			);
			assign addr_lo = aligned_addr[$clog2(width_p) - 1:0];
		end
		else begin : aligned
			wire [(((half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) - 1) >= 0 ? (2 * (half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1))) + -1 : (2 * (2 - (half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)))) + (((half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) - 1) - 1)):(((half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : (half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) - 1)] addrs;
			wire [1:0] vs;
			bsg_encode_one_hot #(.width_p(half_width_lp)) left(
				.i(i[0+:half_width_lp]),
				.addr_o(addrs[(((half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : (half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) - 1)+:(((half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) - 1) >= 0 ? (half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) : 2 - (half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)))]),
				.v_o(vs[0])
			);
			bsg_encode_one_hot #(.width_p(half_width_lp)) right(
				.i(i[half_width_lp+:half_width_lp]),
				.addr_o(addrs[(((half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : (half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) - 1) + (((half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) - 1) >= 0 ? (half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) : 2 - (half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)))+:(((half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) - 1) >= 0 ? (half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) : 2 - (half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)))]),
				.v_o(vs[1])
			);
			assign v_o = |vs;
			if (width_p == 2) assign addr_lo = vs[lo_to_hi_p];
			else assign addr_lo = {vs[lo_to_hi_p], addrs[(((half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : (half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) - 1)+:(((half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) - 1) >= 0 ? (half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) : 2 - (half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)))] | addrs[(((half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : (half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) - 1) + (((half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) - 1) >= 0 ? (half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) : 2 - (half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)))+:(((half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) - 1) >= 0 ? (half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)) : 2 - (half_width_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p >> 1)))]};
		end
	endgenerate
	assign addr_o = (((i - 1) & i) == 1'sb0 ? addr_lo : {(width_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p)) {1'bx}});
endmodule
module bsg_mux (
	data_i,
	sel_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter width_p = "inv";
	parameter els_p = 1;
	parameter harden_p = 0;
	parameter balanced_p = 0;
	parameter lg_els_lp = (els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(els_p));
	input [((els_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (els_p * width_p) + -1 : (els_p * (2 - width_p)) + ((width_p - 1) - 1)) : ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((2 - els_p) * width_p) + (((els_p - 1) * width_p) - 1) : ((2 - els_p) * (2 - width_p)) + (((width_p - 1) + ((els_p - 1) * (2 - width_p))) - 1))):((els_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) : ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (els_p - 1) * width_p : (width_p - 1) + ((els_p - 1) * (2 - width_p))))] data_i;
	input [lg_els_lp - 1:0] sel_i;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	assign data_o = data_i[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) + (((els_p - 1) >= 0 ? sel_i : 0 - (sel_i - (els_p - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p))+:((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)];
	initial ;
endmodule
module bsg_mux_one_hot (
	data_i,
	sel_one_hot_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter width_p = "inv";
	parameter els_p = 1;
	parameter harden_p = 1;
	input [((els_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (els_p * width_p) + -1 : (els_p * (2 - width_p)) + ((width_p - 1) - 1)) : ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((2 - els_p) * width_p) + (((els_p - 1) * width_p) - 1) : ((2 - els_p) * (2 - width_p)) + (((width_p - 1) + ((els_p - 1) * (2 - width_p))) - 1))):((els_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) : ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (els_p - 1) * width_p : (width_p - 1) + ((els_p - 1) * (2 - width_p))))] data_i;
	input [els_p - 1:0] sel_one_hot_i;
	output [width_p - 1:0] data_o;
	wire [((els_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (els_p * width_p) + -1 : (els_p * (2 - width_p)) + ((width_p - 1) - 1)) : ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((2 - els_p) * width_p) + (((els_p - 1) * width_p) - 1) : ((2 - els_p) * (2 - width_p)) + (((width_p - 1) + ((els_p - 1) * (2 - width_p))) - 1))):((els_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) : ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (els_p - 1) * width_p : (width_p - 1) + ((els_p - 1) * (2 - width_p))))] data_masked;
	genvar i;
	genvar j;
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < els_p; i = i + 1) begin : mask
			assign data_masked[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) + (((els_p - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (els_p - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p))+:((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)] = data_i[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) + (((els_p - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (els_p - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p))+:((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)] & {width_p {sel_one_hot_i[i]}};
		end
	endgenerate
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < width_p; i = i + 1) begin : reduce
			wire [els_p - 1:0] gather;
			for (j = 0; j < els_p; j = j + 1) assign gather[j] = data_masked[(((els_p - 1) >= 0 ? j : 0 - (j - (els_p - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)) + ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (width_p - 1)))];
			assign data_o[i] = |gather;
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_mux_segmented (
	data0_i,
	data1_i,
	sel_i,
	data_o
);
	parameter segments_p = "inv";
	parameter segment_width_p = "inv";
	parameter data_width_lp = segments_p * segment_width_p;
	input [data_width_lp - 1:0] data0_i;
	input [data_width_lp - 1:0] data1_i;
	input [segments_p - 1:0] sel_i;
	output wire [data_width_lp - 1:0] data_o;
	genvar i;
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < segments_p; i = i + 1) assign data_o[i * segment_width_p+:segment_width_p] = (sel_i[i] ? data1_i[i * segment_width_p+:segment_width_p] : data0_i[i * segment_width_p+:segment_width_p]);
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_priority_encode (
	i,
	addr_o,
	v_o
);
	parameter width_p = "inv";
	parameter lo_to_hi_p = "inv";
	input [width_p - 1:0] i;
	output [(width_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(width_p)) - 1:0] addr_o;
	output v_o;
	wire [width_p - 1:0] enc_lo;
	bsg_priority_encode_one_hot_out #(
		.width_p(width_p),
		.lo_to_hi_p(lo_to_hi_p)
	) a(
		.i(i),
		.o(enc_lo)
	);
	bsg_encode_one_hot #(
		.width_p(width_p),
		.lo_to_hi_p(lo_to_hi_p)
	) b(
		.i(enc_lo),
		.addr_o(addr_o),
		.v_o(v_o)
	);
endmodule
module bsg_priority_encode_one_hot_out (
	i,
	o
);
	parameter width_p = "inv";
	parameter lo_to_hi_p = "inv";
	input [width_p - 1:0] i;
	output [width_p - 1:0] o;
	wire [width_p - 1:0] scan_lo;
	generate
		if (width_p == 1) assign o = i;
		else begin
			bsg_scan #(
				.width_p(width_p),
				.or_p(1),
				.lo_to_hi_p(lo_to_hi_p)
			) scan(
				.i(i),
				.o(scan_lo)
			);
			if (lo_to_hi_p) assign o = scan_lo & {~scan_lo[width_p - 2:0], 1'b1};
			else assign o = scan_lo & {1'b1, ~scan_lo[width_p - 1:1]};
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_round_robin_arb (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	grants_en_i,
	reqs_i,
	grants_o,
	sel_one_hot_o,
	v_o,
	tag_o,
	yumi_i
);
	parameter inputs_p = -1;
	parameter lg_inputs_p = (inputs_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(inputs_p));
	parameter reset_on_sr_p = 1'b0;
	parameter hold_on_sr_p = 1'b0;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input grants_en_i;
	input [inputs_p - 1:0] reqs_i;
	output wire [inputs_p - 1:0] grants_o;
	output wire [inputs_p - 1:0] sel_one_hot_o;
	output v_o;
	output reg [lg_inputs_p - 1:0] tag_o;
	input yumi_i;
	wire [lg_inputs_p - 1:0] last;
	reg [lg_inputs_p - 1:0] last_n;
	reg [lg_inputs_p - 1:0] last_r;
	reg hold_on_sr;
	wire reset_on_sr;
	generate
		if (inputs_p == 1) begin : inputs_1
			reg [0:0] sel_one_hot_n;
			always @(*)
				casez ({last_r, reqs_i})
					2'b?_0: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 1'b0;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					2'b0_1: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 1'b1;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					default: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 1'bx;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
				endcase
			assign sel_one_hot_o = sel_one_hot_n;
			assign grants_o = sel_one_hot_n & grants_en_i;
			if (hold_on_sr_p) always @(*)
				casez (last_r)
					1'b0: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 1'b1;
					default: hold_on_sr = 1'b0;
				endcase
			else begin : not_hold_on_sr_p
				always @(*) hold_on_sr = 1'sb0;
			end
			if (reset_on_sr_p) begin : reset_on_1
				assign reset_on_sr = reqs_i == 1'b1;
			end
			else begin : not_reset_on_sr_p
				assign reset_on_sr = 1'sb0;
			end
		end
	endgenerate
	generate
		if (inputs_p == 2) begin : inputs_2
			reg [1:0] sel_one_hot_n;
			always @(*)
				casez ({last_r, reqs_i})
					3'b?_00: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 2'b00;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					3'b0_1?: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 2'b10;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					3'b0_01: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 2'b01;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					3'b1_?1: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 2'b01;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					3'b1_10: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 2'b10;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					default: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = {2 {1'bx}};
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
				endcase
			assign sel_one_hot_o = sel_one_hot_n;
			assign grants_o = sel_one_hot_n & {2 {grants_en_i}};
			if (hold_on_sr_p) always @(*)
				casez (last_r)
					1'b0: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 2'b01;
					default: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 2'b10;
				endcase
			else begin : not_hold_on_sr_p
				always @(*) hold_on_sr = 1'sb0;
			end
			if (reset_on_sr_p) begin : reset_on_2
				assign reset_on_sr = (reqs_i == 2'b01) | (reqs_i == 2'b10);
			end
			else begin : not_reset_on_sr_p
				assign reset_on_sr = 1'sb0;
			end
		end
	endgenerate
	generate
		if (inputs_p == 3) begin : inputs_3
			reg [2:0] sel_one_hot_n;
			always @(*)
				casez ({last_r, reqs_i})
					5'b??_000: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					5'b00_?1?: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b010;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					5'b00_10?: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b100;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(2);
					end
					5'b00_001: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b001;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					5'b01_1??: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b100;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(2);
					end
					5'b01_0?1: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b001;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					5'b01_010: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b010;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					5'b10_??1: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b001;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					5'b10_?10: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b010;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					5'b10_100: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 3'b100;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(2);
					end
					default: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = {3 {1'bx}};
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
				endcase
			assign sel_one_hot_o = sel_one_hot_n;
			assign grants_o = sel_one_hot_n & {3 {grants_en_i}};
			if (hold_on_sr_p) always @(*)
				casez (last_r)
					2'b00: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 3'b010;
					2'b01: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 3'b001;
					2'b10: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 3'b100;
					default: hold_on_sr = 1'b0;
				endcase
			else begin : not_hold_on_sr_p
				always @(*) hold_on_sr = 1'sb0;
			end
			if (reset_on_sr_p) begin : reset_on_3
				assign reset_on_sr = ((reqs_i == 3'b010) | (reqs_i == 3'b001)) | (reqs_i == 3'b100);
			end
			else begin : not_reset_on_sr_p
				assign reset_on_sr = 1'sb0;
			end
		end
	endgenerate
	generate
		if (inputs_p == 4) begin : inputs_4
			reg [3:0] sel_one_hot_n;
			always @(*)
				casez ({last_r, reqs_i})
					6'b??_0000: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 4'b0000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					6'b00_??1?: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 4'b0010;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					6'b00_?10?: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 4'b0100;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(2);
					end
					6'b00_100?: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 4'b1000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(3);
					end
					6'b00_0001: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 4'b0001;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					6'b01_?1??: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 4'b0100;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(2);
					end
					6'b01_10??: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 4'b1000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(3);
					end
					6'b01_00?1: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 4'b0001;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					6'b01_0010: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 4'b0010;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					6'b10_1???: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 4'b1000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(3);
					end
					6'b10_0??1: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 4'b0001;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					6'b10_0?10: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 4'b0010;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					6'b10_0100: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 4'b0100;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(2);
					end
					6'b11_???1: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 4'b0001;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					6'b11_??10: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 4'b0010;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					6'b11_?100: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 4'b0100;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(2);
					end
					6'b11_1000: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 4'b1000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(3);
					end
					default: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = {4 {1'bx}};
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
				endcase
			assign sel_one_hot_o = sel_one_hot_n;
			assign grants_o = sel_one_hot_n & {4 {grants_en_i}};
			if (hold_on_sr_p) always @(*)
				casez (last_r)
					2'b00: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 4'b0100;
					2'b01: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 4'b0010;
					2'b10: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 4'b0001;
					default: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 4'b1000;
				endcase
			else begin : not_hold_on_sr_p
				always @(*) hold_on_sr = 1'sb0;
			end
			if (reset_on_sr_p) begin : reset_on_4
				assign reset_on_sr = (((reqs_i == 4'b0100) | (reqs_i == 4'b0010)) | (reqs_i == 4'b0001)) | (reqs_i == 4'b1000);
			end
			else begin : not_reset_on_sr_p
				assign reset_on_sr = 1'sb0;
			end
		end
	endgenerate
	generate
		if (inputs_p == 5) begin : inputs_5
			reg [4:0] sel_one_hot_n;
			always @(*)
				casez ({last_r, reqs_i})
					8'b???_00000: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b00000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					8'b000_???1?: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b00010;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					8'b000_??10?: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b00100;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(2);
					end
					8'b000_?100?: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b01000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(3);
					end
					8'b000_1000?: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b10000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(4);
					end
					8'b000_00001: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b00001;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					8'b001_??1??: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b00100;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(2);
					end
					8'b001_?10??: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b01000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(3);
					end
					8'b001_100??: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b10000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(4);
					end
					8'b001_000?1: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b00001;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					8'b001_00010: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b00010;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					8'b010_?1???: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b01000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(3);
					end
					8'b010_10???: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b10000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(4);
					end
					8'b010_00??1: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b00001;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					8'b010_00?10: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b00010;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					8'b010_00100: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b00100;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(2);
					end
					8'b011_1????: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b10000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(4);
					end
					8'b011_0???1: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b00001;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					8'b011_0??10: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b00010;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					8'b011_0?100: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b00100;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(2);
					end
					8'b011_01000: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b01000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(3);
					end
					8'b100_????1: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b00001;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					8'b100_???10: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b00010;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					8'b100_??100: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b00100;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(2);
					end
					8'b100_?1000: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b01000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(3);
					end
					8'b100_10000: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 5'b10000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(4);
					end
					default: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = {5 {1'bx}};
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
				endcase
			assign sel_one_hot_o = sel_one_hot_n;
			assign grants_o = sel_one_hot_n & {5 {grants_en_i}};
			if (hold_on_sr_p) always @(*)
				casez (last_r)
					3'b000: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 5'b01000;
					3'b001: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 5'b00100;
					3'b010: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 5'b00010;
					3'b011: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 5'b00001;
					3'b100: hold_on_sr = reqs_i == 5'b10000;

			else begin : not_hold_on_sr_p

			end
			else begin : not_reset_on_sr_p
				assign reset_on_sr = 1'sb0;
			end
		end
	endgenerate
	generate
		if (inputs_p == 6) begin : inputs_6
			reg [5:0] sel_one_hot_n;
			always @(*)
				casez ({last_r, reqs_i})
					9'b???_000000: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b000000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					9'b000_????1?: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b000010;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					9'b000_???10?: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b000100;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(2);
					end
					9'b000_??100?: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b001000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(3);
					end
					9'b000_?1000?: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b010000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(4);
					end
					9'b000_10000?: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b100000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(5);
					end
					9'b000_000001: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b000001;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					9'b001_???1??: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b000100;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(2);
					end
					9'b001_??10??: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b001000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(3);
					end
					9'b001_?100??: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b010000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(4);
					end
					9'b001_1000??: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b100000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(5);
					end
					9'b001_0000?1: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b000001;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					9'b001_000010: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b000010;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					9'b010_??1???: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b001000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(3);
					end
					9'b010_?10???: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b010000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(4);
					end
					9'b010_100???: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b100000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(5);
					end
					9'b010_000??1: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b000001;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					9'b010_000?10: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b000010;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					9'b010_000100: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b000100;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(2);
					end
					9'b011_?1????: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b010000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(4);
					end
					9'b011_10????: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b100000;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(5);
					end
					9'b011_00???1: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b000001;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(0);
					end
					9'b011_00??10: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b000010;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(1);
					end
					9'b011_00?100: begin
						sel_one_hot_n = 6'b000100;
						tag_o = sv2v_cast_8141E(2);
					end
					9'b011_001000: begin

			for (i = N; i <= S; i = i + 1) begin
				assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? N : 0 - (N - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = (i == N ? 1'b0 : (v_i_stub[i] & x_eq[i]) & y_lt[i]);
				assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? S : 0 - (S - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = (i == S ? 1'b0 : (v_i_stub[i] & x_eq[i]) & y_gt[i]);
			end
			assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? E : 0 - (E - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = v_i_stub[P] & x_gt[P];
			assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? W : 0 - (W - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = v_i_stub[P] & x_lt[P];
			assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = (v_i_stub[P] & x_eq[P]) & y_eq[P];
			assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? S : 0 - (S - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = (v_i_stub[P] & x_eq[P]) & y_gt[P];
			assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? N : 0 - (N - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = (v_i_stub[P] & x_eq[P]) & y_lt[P];
			for (i = W; i <= S; i = i + 1) assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = (v_i_stub[i] & x_eq[i]) & y_eq[i];
			always @(negedge clk_i)
				;
		end
		else begin : YX_dor
			for (i = W; i <= E; i = i + 1) begin : x2y
				assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? N : 0 - (N - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = 1'b0;
				assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? S : 0 - (S - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = 1'b0;
			end
			for (i = N; i <= S; i = i + 1) begin : y2x
				assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? W : 0 - (W - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = (v_i_stub[i] & y_eq[i]) & x_lt[i];
				assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? E : 0 - (E - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = (v_i_stub[i] & y_eq[i]) & x_gt[i];
			end
			for (i = N; i <= S; i = i + 1) begin
				assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? N : 0 - (N - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = (i == N ? 1'b0 : v_i_stub[i] & y_lt[i]);
				assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? S : 0 - (S - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = (i == S ? 1'b0 : v_i_stub[i] & y_gt[i]);
			end
			for (i = W; i <= E; i = i + 1) begin
				assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? W : 0 - (W - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = (i == W ? 1'b0 : (v_i_stub[i] & y_eq[i]) & x_lt[i]);
				assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? E : 0 - (E - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = (i == E ? 1'b0 : (v_i_stub[i] & y_eq[i]) & x_gt[i]);
			end
			assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? S : 0 - (S - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = v_i_stub[P] & y_gt[P];
			assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? N : 0 - (N - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = v_i_stub[P] & y_lt[P];
			assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = (v_i_stub[P] & x_eq[P]) & y_eq[P];
			assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? E : 0 - (E - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = (v_i_stub[P] & y_eq[P]) & x_gt[P];
			assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? W : 0 - (W - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = (v_i_stub[P] & y_eq[P]) & x_lt[P];
			for (i = W; i <= S; i = i + 1) assign req_o[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1)))] = (v_i_stub[i] & x_eq[i]) & y_eq[i];
			always @(negedge clk_i)
				;
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_mesh_router (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	data_i,
	v_i,
	yumi_o,
	ready_i,
	data_o,
	v_o,
	my_x_i,
	my_y_i
);
	localparam [2:0] P = 3'd0;
	localparam [2:0] W = 3'd0 + 1;
	localparam [2:0] E = 3'd0 + 2;
	localparam [2:0] N = 3'd0 + 3;
	localparam [2:0] S = 3'd0 + 4;
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter x_cord_width_p = -1;
	parameter y_cord_width_p = -1;
	parameter debug_p = 0;
	parameter dirs_lp = 5;
	parameter stub_p = {dirs_lp {1'b0}};
	parameter XY_order_p = 1;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (dirs_lp * width_p) + -1 : (dirs_lp * (2 - width_p)) + ((width_p - 1) - 1)) : ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((2 - dirs_lp) * width_p) + (((dirs_lp - 1) * width_p) - 1) : ((2 - dirs_lp) * (2 - width_p)) + (((width_p - 1) + ((dirs_lp - 1) * (2 - width_p))) - 1))):((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) : ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (dirs_lp - 1) * width_p : (width_p - 1) + ((dirs_lp - 1) * (2 - width_p))))] data_i;
	input [dirs_lp - 1:0] v_i;
	output wire [dirs_lp - 1:0] yumi_o;
	input [dirs_lp - 1:0] ready_i;
	output [((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (dirs_lp * width_p) + -1 : (dirs_lp * (2 - width_p)) + ((width_p - 1) - 1)) : ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((2 - dirs_lp) * width_p) + (((dirs_lp - 1) * width_p) - 1) : ((2 - dirs_lp) * (2 - width_p)) + (((width_p - 1) + ((dirs_lp - 1) * (2 - width_p))) - 1))):((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) : ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (dirs_lp - 1) * width_p : (width_p - 1) + ((dirs_lp - 1) * (2 - width_p))))] data_o;
	output wire [dirs_lp - 1:0] v_o;
	input [x_cord_width_p - 1:0] my_x_i;
	input [y_cord_width_p - 1:0] my_y_i;
	wire [((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? ((x_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (dirs_lp * x_cord_width_p) + -1 : (dirs_lp * (2 - x_cord_width_p)) + ((x_cord_width_p - 1) - 1)) : ((x_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((2 - dirs_lp) * x_cord_width_p) + (((dirs_lp - 1) * x_cord_width_p) - 1) : ((2 - dirs_lp) * (2 - x_cord_width_p)) + (((x_cord_width_p - 1) + ((dirs_lp - 1) * (2 - x_cord_width_p))) - 1))):((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? ((x_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : x_cord_width_p - 1) : ((x_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (dirs_lp - 1) * x_cord_width_p : (x_cord_width_p - 1) + ((dirs_lp - 1) * (2 - x_cord_width_p))))] x_dirs;
	wire [((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? ((y_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (dirs_lp * y_cord_width_p) + -1 : (dirs_lp * (2 - y_cord_width_p)) + ((y_cord_width_p - 1) - 1)) : ((y_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((2 - dirs_lp) * y_cord_width_p) + (((dirs_lp - 1) * y_cord_width_p) - 1) : ((2 - dirs_lp) * (2 - y_cord_width_p)) + (((y_cord_width_p - 1) + ((dirs_lp - 1) * (2 - y_cord_width_p))) - 1))):((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? ((y_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : y_cord_width_p - 1) : ((y_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (dirs_lp - 1) * y_cord_width_p : (y_cord_width_p - 1) + ((dirs_lp - 1) * (2 - y_cord_width_p))))] y_dirs;
	wire [dirs_lp - 1:0] ready_i_stub = ready_i | stub_p;
	wire [dirs_lp - 1:0] v_i_stub = v_i & ~stub_p;
	genvar i;
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < dirs_lp; i = i + 1) begin : reshape
			assign x_dirs[((x_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : x_cord_width_p - 1) + (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((x_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? x_cord_width_p : 2 - x_cord_width_p))+:((x_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? x_cord_width_p : 2 - x_cord_width_p)] = data_i[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)) + ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) : (((((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)) + ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1)) - x_cord_width_p) + 1)+:x_cord_width_p];
			assign y_dirs[((y_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : y_cord_width_p - 1) + (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((y_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? y_cord_width_p : 2 - y_cord_width_p))+:((y_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? y_cord_width_p : 2 - y_cord_width_p)] = data_i[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)) + ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? x_cord_width_p : 0 - (x_cord_width_p - (width_p - 1))) : (((((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)) + ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? x_cord_width_p : 0 - (x_cord_width_p - (width_p - 1)))) - y_cord_width_p) + 1)+:y_cord_width_p];
		end
	endgenerate
	wire [((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? (dirs_lp * dirs_lp) + -1 : (dirs_lp * (2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) - 1)) : ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? ((2 - dirs_lp) * dirs_lp) + (((dirs_lp - 1) * dirs_lp) - 1) : ((2 - dirs_lp) * (2 - dirs_lp)) + (((dirs_lp - 1) + ((dirs_lp - 1) * (2 - dirs_lp))) - 1))):((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : dirs_lp - 1) : ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? (dirs_lp - 1) * dirs_lp : (dirs_lp - 1) + ((dirs_lp - 1) * (2 - dirs_lp))))] req;
	bsg_mesh_router_dor_decoder #(
		.x_cord_width_p(x_cord_width_p),
		.y_cord_width_p(y_cord_width_p),
		.dirs_lp(dirs_lp),
		.XY_order_p(XY_order_p)
	) dor_decoder(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.v_i(v_i_stub),
		.my_x_i(my_x_i),
		.my_y_i(my_y_i),
		.x_dirs_i(x_dirs),
		.y_dirs_i(y_dirs),
		.req_o(req)
	);
	wire P_gnt_p;
	wire P_gnt_e;
	wire P_gnt_s;
	wire P_gnt_n;
	wire P_gnt_w;
	wire W_gnt_e;
	wire W_gnt_p;
	wire E_gnt_w;
	wire E_gnt_p;
	wire N_gnt_s;
	wire N_gnt_p;
	wire S_gnt_n;
	wire S_gnt_p;
	wire N_gnt_e;
	wire N_gnt_w;
	wire S_gnt_e;
	wire S_gnt_w;
	wire W_gnt_n;
	wire W_gnt_s;
	wire E_gnt_n;
	wire E_gnt_s;
	wire P_sel_p;
	wire P_sel_e;
	wire P_sel_s;
	wire P_sel_n;
	wire P_sel_w;
	wire W_sel_e;
	wire W_sel_p;
	wire E_sel_w;
	wire E_sel_p;
	wire N_sel_s;
	wire N_sel_p;
	wire S_sel_n;
	wire S_sel_p;
	wire N_sel_e;
	wire N_sel_w;
	wire S_sel_e;
	wire S_sel_w;
	wire W_sel_n;
	wire W_sel_s;
	wire E_sel_n;
	wire E_sel_s;
	generate
		if (XY_order_p == 1) begin
			bsg_round_robin_arb #(.inputs_p(2)) west_rr_arb(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.grants_en_i(ready_i_stub[W]),
				.reqs_i({req[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? E : 0 - (E - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? W : 0 - (W - (dirs_lp - 1)))], req[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? W : 0 - (W - (dirs_lp - 1)))]}),
				.grants_o({W_gnt_e, W_gnt_p}),
				.sel_one_hot_o({W_sel_e, W_sel_p}),
				.v_o(v_o[W]),
				.tag_o(),
				.yumi_i(v_o[W] & ready_i_stub[W])
			);
			bsg_mux_one_hot #(
				.width_p(width_p),
				.els_p(2)
			) mux_data_west(
				.data_i({data_i[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) + (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p))+:((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)], data_i[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) + (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? E : 0 - (E - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p))+:((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)]}),
				.sel_one_hot_i({W_sel_p, W_sel_e}),
				.data_o(data_o[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) + (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? W : 0 - (W - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p))+:((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)])
			);
			assign W_gnt_n = 1'b0;
			assign W_gnt_s = 1'b0;
		end
		else begin
			bsg_round_robin_arb #(.inputs_p(4)) west_rr_arb(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.grants_en_i(ready_i_stub[W]),
				.reqs_i({req[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? E : 0 - (E - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? W : 0 - (W - (dirs_lp - 1)))], req[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? W : 0 - (W - (dirs_lp - 1)))], req[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? N : 0 - (N - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? W : 0 - (W - (dirs_lp - 1)))], req[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? S : 0 - (S - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? W : 0 - (W - (dirs_lp - 1)))]}),
				.grants_o({W_gnt_e, W_gnt_p, W_gnt_n, W_gnt_s}),
				.sel_one_hot_o({W_sel_e, W_sel_p, W_sel_n, W_sel_s}),
				.v_o(v_o[W]),
				.tag_o(),
				.yumi_i(v_o[W] & ready_i_stub[W])
			);
			bsg_mux_one_hot #(
				.width_p(width_p),
				.els_p(4)
			) mux_data_west(
				.data_i({data_i[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) + (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p))+:((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)], data_i[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) + (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? E : 0 - (E - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p))+:((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)], data_i[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) + (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? N : 0 - (N - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p))+:((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)], data_i[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) + (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? S : 0 - (S - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p))+:((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)]}),
				.sel_one_hot_i({W_sel_p, W_sel_e, W_sel_n, W_sel_s}),
				.data_o(data_o[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) + (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? W : 0 - (W - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p))+:((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)])
			);
		end
	endgenerate
	generate
		if (XY_order_p == 1) begin
			bsg_round_robin_arb #(.inputs_p(2)) east_rr_arb(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.grants_en_i(ready_i_stub[E]),
				.reqs_i({req[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? W : 0 - (W - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? E : 0 - (E - (dirs_lp - 1)))], req[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? E : 0 - (E - (dirs_lp - 1)))]}),
				.grants_o({E_gnt_w, E_gnt_p}),
				.sel_one_hot_o({E_sel_w, E_sel_p}),
				.v_o(v_o[E]),
				.tag_o(),
				.yumi_i(v_o[E] & ready_i_stub[E])
			);
			bsg_mux_one_hot #(
				.width_p(width_p),
				.els_p(2)
			) mux_data_east(

N : 0 - (N - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1)))], req[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? W : 0 - (W - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1)))], req[(((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)) + ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1)))]}),

		.data_i({data_i[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) + (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? P : 0 - (P - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p))+:((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)], data_i[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) + (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? E : 0 - (E - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p))+:((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)], data_i[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) + (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? 	generate
		if (XY_order_p == 1) begin
			assign yumi_o[W] = ((E_gnt_w | N_gnt_w) | S_gnt_w) | P_gnt_w;
			assign yumi_o[E] = ((W_gnt_e | N_gnt_e) | S_gnt_e) | P_gnt_e;
			assign yumi_o[N] = S_gnt_n | P_gnt_n;
			assign yumi_o[S] = N_gnt_s | P_gnt_s;
		end
		else begin
			assign yumi_o[W] = E_gnt_w | P_gnt_w;
			assign yumi_o[E] = W_gnt_e | P_gnt_e;
			assign yumi_o[N] = ((S_gnt_n | W_gnt_n) | E_gnt_n) | P_gnt_n;
			assign yumi_o[S] = ((N_gnt_s | W_gnt_s) | E_gnt_s) | P_gnt_s;
		end
	endgenerate
	generate
		if (debug_p) for (i = P; i <= S; i = i + 1) begin : rof
			wire [2:0] dir = sv2v_cast_3(i);
			always @(negedge clk_i) begin
				if (v_i_stub[i])
					$display("%m wants to send %x to {x,y}={%x,%x} from dir %s, req[SNEWP] = %b, ready_i[SNEWP] = %b", data_i[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) + (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p))+:((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)], x_dirs[((x_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : x_cord_width_p - 1) + (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((x_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? x_cord_width_p : 2 - x_cord_width_p))+:((x_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? x_cord_width_p : 2 - x_cord_width_p)], y_dirs[((y_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : y_cord_width_p - 1) + (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((y_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? y_cord_width_p : 2 - y_cord_width_p))+:((y_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? y_cord_width_p : 2 - y_cord_width_p)], dir.name(), req[((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : dirs_lp - 1) + (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp))+:((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? dirs_lp : 2 - dirs_lp)], ready_i_stub);
				if (v_o[i])
					$display("%m sending %x in dir %s", data_o[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) + (((dirs_lp - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (dirs_lp - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p))+:((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)], dir.name());
			end
		end
	endgenerate
	function automatic [2:0] sv2v_cast_3;
		input reg [2:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_3 = inp;
	endfunction
endmodule
module bsg_mesh_router_buffered (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	link_i,
	link_o,
	my_x_i,
	my_y_i
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter x_cord_width_p = -1;
	parameter y_cord_width_p = -1;
	parameter debug_p = 0;
	parameter dirs_lp = 5;
	parameter stub_p = {dirs_lp {1'b0}};
	parameter XY_order_p = 1;
	parameter bsg_ready_and_link_sif_width_lp = width_p + 2;
	parameter repeater_output_p = {dirs_lp {1'b0}};
	input clk_i;

		sv2v_cast_EF442 = inp;

module bsg_wormhole_router_adapter_out (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	link_i,
	link_o,
	packet_o,
	v_o,
	yumi_i
);
	parameter max_payload_width_p = "inv";
	parameter len_width_p = "inv";
	parameter cord_width_p = "inv";
	parameter flit_width_p = "inv";
	localparam bsg_ready_and_link_sif_width_lp = flit_width_p + 2;
	localparam bsg_wormhole_packet_width_lp = (cord_width_p + len_width_p) + max_payload_width_p;
	input clk_i;

	wire [(2 + ((flit_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? flit_width_p : 2 - flit_width_p)) - 1:0] link_cast_o;

	assign link_o = link_cast_o;
	wire [(((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p) + ((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p)) - 1:0] header_li;
	assign header_li = link_cast_i[((flit_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? flit_width_p : 2 - flit_width_p) + -1-:((((flit_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? flit_width_p : 2 - flit_width_p) + -1) >= 0 ? ((flit_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? flit_width_p : 2 - flit_width_p) : 1 - (((flit_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? flit_width_p : 2 - flit_width_p) + -1))];
	localparam max_num_flits_lp = ((((((((max_payload_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? max_payload_width_p : 2 - max_payload_width_p) + ((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p)) + ((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p)) - 1) >= 0 ? (((max_payload_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? max_payload_width_p : 2 - max_payload_width_p) + ((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p)) + ((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p) : 2 - ((((max_payload_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? max_payload_width_p : 2 - max_payload_width_p) + ((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p)) + ((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p))) + flit_width_p) - 1) / flit_width_p;
	localparam protocol_len_lp = (max_num_flits_lp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(((((((((max_payload_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? max_payload_width_p : 2 - max_payload_width_p) + ((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p)) + ((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p)) - 1) >= 0 ? (((max_payload_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? max_payload_width_p : 2 - max_payload_width_p) + ((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p)) + ((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p) : 2 - ((((max_payload_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? max_payload_width_p : 2 - max_payload_width_p) + ((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p)) + ((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p))) + flit_width_p) - 1) / flit_width_p));
	wire [(max_num_flits_lp * flit_width_p) - 1:0] packet_padded_lo;
	bsg_serial_in_parallel_out_dynamic #(
		.width_p(flit_width_p),
		.max_els_p(max_num_flits_lp)
	) sipo(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.data_i(link_cast_i[((flit_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? flit_width_p : 2 - flit_width_p) + -1-:((((flit_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? flit_width_p : 2 - flit_width_p) + -1) >= 0 ? ((flit_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? flit_width_p : 2 - flit_width_p) : 1 - (((flit_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? flit_width_p : 2 - flit_width_p) + -1))]),
		.len_i(sv2v_cast_EF442(header_li[((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p) + (((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p) + -1)-:((((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p) + (((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p) + -1)) >= ((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p) ? ((((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p) + (((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p) + -1)) - ((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p)) + 1 : (((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p) - (((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p) + (((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p) + -1))) + 1)])),
		.ready_o(link_cast_o[1 + (((flit_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? flit_width_p : 2 - flit_width_p) + -1)]),
		.len_ready_o(),
		.v_i(link_cast_i[1 + (1 + (((flit_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? flit_width_p : 2 - flit_width_p) + -1))]),
		.v_o(v_o),
		.data_o(packet_padded_lo),
		.yumi_i(yumi_i)
	);
	assign packet_o = packet_padded_lo[0+:bsg_wormhole_packet_width_lp];
	assign link_cast_o[((flit_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? flit_width_p : 2 - flit_width_p) + -1-:((((flit_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? flit_width_p : 2 - flit_width_p) + -1) >= 0 ? ((flit_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? flit_width_p : 2 - flit_width_p) : 1 - (((flit_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? flit_width_p : 2 - flit_width_p) + -1))] = 1'sb0;
	assign link_cast_o[1 + (1 + (((flit_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? flit_width_p : 2 - flit_width_p) + -1))] = 1'sb0;
	wire recv_r;
	bsg_dff_reset_en #(.width_p(1)) recv_reg(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.en_i(link_cast_i[1 + (1 + (((flit_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? flit_width_p : 2 - flit_width_p) + -1))] || yumi_i),
		.data_i(link_cast_i[1 + (1 + (((flit_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? flit_width_p : 2 - flit_width_p) + -1))]),
		.data_o(recv_r)
	);
	wire new_header_li = ~recv_r & link_cast_i[1 + (1 + (((flit_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? flit_width_p : 2 - flit_width_p) + -1))];
	function automatic [((((((((((max_payload_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? max_payload_width_p : 2 - max_payload_width_p) + ((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p)) + ((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p)) - 1) >= 0 ? (((max_payload_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? max_payload_width_p : 2 - max_payload_width_p) + ((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p)) + ((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p) : 2 - ((((max_payload_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? max_payload_width_p : 2 - max_payload_width_p) + ((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p)) + ((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p))) + flit_width_p) - 1) / flit_width_p) == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(((((((((max_payload_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? max_payload_width_p : 2 - max_payload_width_p) + ((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p)) + ((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p)) - 1) >= 0 ? (((max_payload_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? max_payload_width_p : 2 - max_payload_width_p) + ((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p)) + ((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p) : 2 - ((((max_payload_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? max_payload_width_p : 2 - max_payload_width_p) + ((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p)) + ((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p))) + flit_width_p) - 1) / flit_width_p)) - 1:0] sv2v_cast_EF442;
		input reg [((((((((((max_payload_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? max_payload_width_p : 2 - max_payload_width_p) + ((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p)) + ((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p)) - 1) >= 0 ? (((max_payload_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? max_payload_width_p : 2 - max_payload_width_p) + ((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p)) + ((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p) : 2 - ((((max_payload_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? max_payload_width_p : 2 - max_payload_width_p) + ((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p)) + ((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p))) + flit_width_p) - 1) / flit_width_p) == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(((((((((max_payload_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? max_payload_width_p : 2 - max_payload_width_p) + ((len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? len_width_p : 2 - len_width_p)) + ((cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? cord_width_p : 2 - cord_width_p)) - 1) >= 0 ? 		sv2v_cast_EF442 = inp;

module bsg_flow_counter (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	v_i,
	ready_i,
	yumi_i,
	count_o
);
	parameter els_p = -1;
	parameter count_free_p = 0;
	parameter ready_THEN_valid_p = 0;
	parameter ptr_width_lp = $clog2(els_p + 1);
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input v_i;
	input ready_i;
	input yumi_i;
	output [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] count_o;
	wire enque;
	generate
		if (ready_THEN_valid_p) begin : gen_blk_protocol_select
			assign enque = v_i;
		end
		else begin : gen_blk_protocol_select
			assign enque = v_i & ready_i;
		end
	endgenerate
	generate
		if (count_free_p) begin : gen_blk_0
			bsg_counter_up_down #(
				.max_val_p(els_p),
				.init_val_p(els_p),
				.max_step_p(1)
			) counter(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.up_i(yumi_i),
				.down_i(enque),
				.count_o(count_o)
			);
		end
		else begin : gen_blk_0
			bsg_counter_up_down #(
				.max_val_p(els_p),
				.init_val_p(0),
				.max_step_p(1)
			) counter(
				.clk_i(clk_i),
				.reset_i(reset_i),
				.up_i(enque),
				.down_i(yumi_i),
				.count_o(count_o)
			);
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule
module bsg_serial_in_parallel_out_dynamic (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	v_i,
	len_i,
	data_i,
	ready_o,
	len_ready_o,
	v_o,
	data_o,
	yumi_i
);
	parameter width_p = "inv";
	parameter max_els_p = "inv";
	parameter lg_max_els_lp = (max_els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(max_els_p));
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input v_i;
	input [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] len_i;
	input [width_p - 1:0] data_i;
	output ready_o;
	output len_ready_o;
	output v_o;
	output [((max_els_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (max_els_p * width_p) + -1 : (max_els_p * (2 - width_p)) + ((width_p - 1) - 1)) : ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((2 - max_els_p) * width_p) + (((max_els_p - 1) * width_p) - 1) : ((2 - max_els_p) * (2 - width_p)) + (((width_p - 1) + ((max_els_p - 1) * (2 - width_p))) - 1))):((max_els_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) : ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (max_els_p - 1) * width_p : (width_p - 1) + ((max_els_p - 1) * (2 - width_p))))] data_o;
	input yumi_i;
	genvar i;
	wire yumi_lo;
	assign yumi_lo = v_i & ready_o;
	wire [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] count_r;
	wire [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] count_lo;
	wire [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] len_r;
	wire [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] len_lo;
	wire clear_li;
	wire up_li;
	wire dff_en_li;
	wire go_fifo_v_li;
	wire count_r_is_zero;
	wire count_r_is_last;
	assign count_lo = count_r;
	assign len_lo = (count_r_is_zero ? len_i : len_r);
	assign count_r_is_zero = count_lo == sv2v_cast_C8F51(0);
	assign count_r_is_last = count_lo == len_lo;
	assign len_ready_o = count_r_is_zero;
	assign up_li = yumi_lo & ~count_r_is_last;
	assign clear_li = yumi_lo & count_r_is_last;
	assign go_fifo_v_li = clear_li;
	assign dff_en_li = yumi_lo & count_r_is_zero;
	bsg_counter_clear_up #(
		.max_val_p(max_els_p - 1),
		.init_val_p(0)
	) ctr(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.clear_i(clear_li),
		.up_i(up_li),
		.count_o(count_r)
	);
	bsg_dff_reset_en #(
		.width_p(lg_max_els_lp),
		.reset_val_p(0)
	) dff_len(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.en_i(dff_en_li),
		.data_i(len_i),
		.data_o(len_r)
	);
	wire one_word_lo;
	bsg_two_fifo #(.width_p(1)) go_fifo(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.ready_o(),
		.data_i(count_r_is_zero),
		.v_i(go_fifo_v_li),
		.v_o(v_o),
		.data_o(one_word_lo),
		.yumi_i(yumi_i)
	);
	wire [max_els_p - 1:0] fifo_valid_li;
	wire [max_els_p - 1:0] fifo_ready_lo;
	wire [max_els_p - 1:0] fifo_valid_lo;
	wire [max_els_p - 1:0] fifo_yumi_li;
	assign ready_o = fifo_ready_lo[count_lo];
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < max_els_p; i = i + 1) begin : rof0
			if (i == 0) assign fifo_yumi_li[i] = yumi_i;
			else assign fifo_yumi_li[i] = (fifo_valid_lo[i] & yumi_i) & ~one_word_lo;
		end
	endgenerate
	bsg_decode_with_v #(.num_out_p(max_els_p)) bdwv(
		.i(count_lo),
		.v_i(v_i),
		.o(fifo_valid_li)
	);
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < max_els_p; i = i + 1) begin : fifos
			if (i == 0) begin : twofifo
				bsg_two_fifo #(.width_p(width_p)) fifo(
					.clk_i(clk_i),
					.reset_i(reset_i),
					.ready_o(fifo_ready_lo[i]),
					.data_i(data_i),
					.v_i(fifo_valid_li[i]),
					.v_o(fifo_valid_lo[i]),
					.data_o(data_o[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) + (((max_els_p - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (max_els_p - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p))+:((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)]),
					.yumi_i(fifo_yumi_li[i])
				);
			end
			else begin : onefifo
				bsg_one_fifo #(.width_p(width_p)) fifo(
					.clk_i(clk_i),
					.reset_i(reset_i),
					.ready_o(fifo_ready_lo[i]),
					.data_i(data_i),
					.v_i(fifo_valid_li[i]),
					.v_o(fifo_valid_lo[i]),
					.data_o(data_o[((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) + (((max_els_p - 1) >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - (max_els_p - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p))+:((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)]),
					.yumi_i(fifo_yumi_li[i])
				);
			end
		end
	endgenerate
	function automatic [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] sv2v_cast_C8F51;
		input reg [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_C8F51 = inp;
	endfunction
endmodule
module bsg_parallel_in_serial_out_dynamic (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	v_i,
	len_i,
	data_i,
	ready_o,
	v_o,

	data_o,
	yumi_i
);
	parameter width_p = "inv";
	parameter max_els_p = "inv";
	parameter lg_max_els_lp = (max_els_p == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(max_els_p));

	input v_i;

	output v_o;
	output len_v_o;

	wire [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] len_lo;
	wire [((max_els_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (max_els_p * width_p) + -1 : (max_els_p * (2 - width_p)) + ((width_p - 1) - 1)) : ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((2 - max_els_p) * width_p) + (((max_els_p - 1) * width_p) - 1) : ((2 - max_els_p) * (2 - width_p)) + (((width_p - 1) + ((max_els_p - 1) * (2 - width_p))) - 1))):((max_els_p - 1) >= 0 ? 	bsg_two_fifo #(.width_p(lg_max_els_lp)) go_fifo(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.ready_o(ready_o),
		.data_i(len_i),
		.v_i(v_i),
		.v_o(v_o),
		.data_o(len_lo),
		.yumi_i(go_fifo_yumi_li)
	);
	bsg_two_fifo #(.width_p(max_els_p * width_p)) data_fifo(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.ready_o(),
		.data_i(data_i),
		.v_i(v_i),
		.v_o(),
		.data_o(fifo_data_lo),
		.yumi_i(go_fifo_yumi_li)
	);
	wire [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] count_r;
	wire [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] count_lo;
	wire clear_li;
	wire up_li;
	wire count_r_is_zero;
	wire count_r_is_last;
	assign count_lo = count_r;
	assign count_r_is_zero = count_lo == sv2v_cast_C8F51(0);
	assign count_r_is_last = count_lo == len_lo;
	assign len_v_o = count_r_is_zero;
	assign up_li = yumi_i & ~count_r_is_last;
	assign clear_li = yumi_i & count_r_is_last;
	assign go_fifo_yumi_li = clear_li;
	bsg_counter_clear_up #(
		.max_val_p(max_els_p - 1),
		.init_val_p(0)
	) ctr(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.clear_i(clear_li),
		.up_i(up_li),
		.count_o(count_r)
	);
	bsg_mux #(
		.width_p(width_p),
		.els_p(max_els_p)
	) data_mux(
		.data_i(fifo_data_lo),
		.sel_i(count_lo),
		.data_o(data_o)
	);
	function automatic [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] sv2v_cast_C8F51;
		input reg [lg_max_els_lp - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_C8F51 = inp;
	endfunction
endmodule
module bsg_counter_up_down (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	up_i,
	down_i,
	count_o
);
	parameter max_val_p = -1;
	parameter init_val_p = -1;
	parameter max_step_p = -1;
	parameter step_width_lp = $clog2(max_step_p + 1);
	parameter ptr_width_lp = $clog2(max_val_p + 1);
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [step_width_lp - 1:0] up_i;
	input [step_width_lp - 1:0] down_i;
	output reg [ptr_width_lp - 1:0] count_o;
	always @(posedge clk_i)
		if (reset_i)
			count_o <= init_val_p;
		else
			count_o <= (count_o - down_i) + up_i;
	always @(negedge clk_i) begin
		if (((count_o == max_val_p) & up_i) & (reset_i === 1'b0))
			$display("%m error: counter overflow at time %t", $time);
		if (((count_o == 0) & down_i) & (reset_i === 1'b0))
			$display("%m error: counter underflow at time %t", $time);
	end
endmodule
module bsg_transpose (
	i,
	o
);
	parameter width_p = "inv";
	parameter els_p = "inv";
	input [((els_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (els_p * width_p) + -1 : (els_p * (2 - width_p)) + ((width_p - 1) - 1)) : ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((2 - els_p) * width_p) + (((els_p - 1) * width_p) - 1) : ((2 - els_p) * (2 - width_p)) + (((width_p - 1) + ((els_p - 1) * (2 - width_p))) - 1))):((els_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : width_p - 1) : ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? (els_p - 1) * width_p : (width_p - 1) + ((els_p - 1) * (2 - width_p))))] i;
	output [((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((els_p - 1) >= 0 ? (width_p * els_p) + -1 : (width_p * (2 - els_p)) + ((els_p - 1) - 1)) : ((els_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((2 - width_p) * els_p) + (((width_p - 1) * els_p) - 1) : ((2 - width_p) * (2 - els_p)) + (((els_p - 1) + ((width_p - 1) * (2 - els_p))) - 1))):((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? ((els_p - 1) >= 0 ? 0 : els_p - 1) : ((els_p - 1) >= 0 ? (width_p - 1) * els_p : (els_p - 1) + ((width_p - 1) * (2 - els_p))))] o;
	genvar x;
	genvar y;
	generate
		for (x = 0; x < els_p; x = x + 1) begin : rof
			for (y = 0; y < width_p; y = y + 1) begin : rof2
				assign o[(((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? y : 0 - (y - (width_p - 1))) * ((els_p - 1) >= 0 ? els_p : 2 - els_p)) + ((els_p - 1) >= 0 ? x : 0 - (x - (els_p - 1)))] = i[(((els_p - 1) >= 0 ? x : 0 - (x - (els_p - 1))) * ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? width_p : 2 - width_p)) + ((width_p - 1) >= 0 ? y : 0 - (y - (width_p - 1)))];
			end
		end
	endgenerate
endmodule

module bsg_wormhole_router_decoder_dor (
	target_cord_i,
	my_cord_i,
	req_o
);
	parameter dims_p = 2;
	parameter cord_dims_p = dims_p;
	parameter reverse_order_p = 0;
	parameter signed [(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? ((cord_dims_p + 1) * 32) + -1 : ((1 - cord_dims_p) * 32) + ((cord_dims_p * 32) - 1)):(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? 0 : cord_dims_p * 32)] cord_markers_pos_p = {sv2v_cast_32_signed(5), sv2v_cast_32_signed(4), sv2v_cast_32_signed(0)};
	parameter output_dirs_lp = (2 * dims_p) + 1;
	input [cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : 0 - (dims_p - cord_dims_p)) * 32+:32] - 1:0] target_cord_i;
	input [cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? dims_p : 0 - (dims_p - cord_dims_p)) * 32+:32] - 1:0] my_cord_i;
	output [output_dirs_lp - 1:0] req_o;
	genvar i;
	wire [dims_p - 1:0] eq;
	wire [dims_p - 1:0] lt;
	wire [dims_p - 1:0] gt;
	generate
		for (i = 0; i < dims_p; i = i + 1) begin : rof
			localparam upper_marker_lp = cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? i + 1 : 0 - ((i + 1) - cord_dims_p)) * 32+:32];
			localparam lower_marker_lp = cord_markers_pos_p[(cord_dims_p >= 0 ? i : 0 - (i - cord_dims_p)) * 32+:32];
			localparam local_cord_width_p = upper_marker_lp - lower_marker_lp;
			wire [local_cord_width_p - 1:0] targ_cord = target_cord_i[upper_marker_lp - 1:lower_marker_lp];
			wire [local_cord_width_p - 1:0] my_cord = my_cord_i[upper_marker_lp - 1:lower_marker_lp];
			assign eq[i] = targ_cord == my_cord;
			assign lt[i] = targ_cord < my_cord;
			assign gt[i] = ~eq[i] & ~lt[i];
		end
	endgenerate
	assign req_o[0] = &eq;
	generate
		if (reverse_order_p) begin : rev
			assign req_o[((dims_p - 1) * 2) + 1] = lt[dims_p - 1];
			assign req_o[((dims_p - 1) * 2) + 2] = gt[dims_p - 1];
			if (dims_p > 1) begin : fi1
				for (i = (dims_p - 1) - 1; i >= 0; i = i - 1) begin : rof3
					assign req_o[(i * 2) + 1] = &eq[dims_p - 1:i + 1] & lt[i];
					assign req_o[(i * 2) + 2] = &eq[dims_p - 1:i + 1] & gt[i];
				end
			end
		end
		else begin : fwd
			assign req_o[1] = lt[0];
			assign req_o[2] = gt[0];
			for (i = 1; i < dims_p; i = i + 1) begin : rof2
				assign req_o[(i * 2) + 1] = &eq[i - 1:0] & lt[i];
				assign req_o[(i * 2) + 2] = &eq[i - 1:0] & gt[i];
			end
		end
	endgenerate
	initial ;
	function automatic signed [31:0] sv2v_cast_32_signed;
		input reg signed [31:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_32_signed = inp;
	endfunction
endmodule
module bsg_wormhole_router_input_control (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	fifo_v_i,
	fifo_decoded_dest_i,
	fifo_payload_len_i,
	fifo_yumi_i,
	reqs_o,
	release_o,
	detected_header_o
);
	parameter output_dirs_p = -1;
	parameter payload_len_bits_p = -1;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input fifo_v_i;
	input [output_dirs_p - 1:0] fifo_decoded_dest_i;
	input [payload_len_bits_p - 1:0] fifo_payload_len_i;
	input fifo_yumi_i;
	output [output_dirs_p - 1:0] reqs_o;
	output release_o;
	output detected_header_o;
	wire [payload_len_bits_p - 1:0] payload_ctr_r;
	wire counter_expired = !payload_ctr_r;
	wire fifo_has_hdr = counter_expired & fifo_v_i;
	bsg_counter_set_down #(
		.width_p(payload_len_bits_p),
		.set_and_down_exclusive_p(1'b1)
	) ctr(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.set_i(fifo_yumi_i & counter_expired),
		.val_i(fifo_payload_len_i),
		.down_i(fifo_yumi_i & ~counter_expired),
		.count_r_o(payload_ctr_r)
	);
	assign reqs_o = (fifo_has_hdr ? fifo_decoded_dest_i : 1'sb0);
	assign release_o = counter_expired;
	assign detected_header_o = fifo_has_hdr;
endmodule
module bsg_wormhole_router_output_control (
	clk_i,
	reset_i,
	reqs_i,
	release_i,
	valid_i,
	yumi_o,
	ready_i,
	valid_o,
	data_sel_o
);
	parameter input_dirs_p = -1;
	input clk_i;
	input reset_i;
	input [input_dirs_p - 1:0] reqs_i;
	input [input_dirs_p - 1:0] release_i;
	input [input_dirs_p - 1:0] valid_i;
	output [input_dirs_p - 1:0] yumi_o;
	input ready_i;
	output valid_o;
	output [input_dirs_p - 1:0] data_sel_o;
	wire [input_dirs_p - 1:0] scheduled_r;
	wire [input_dirs_p - 1:0] scheduled_with_release;
	wire [input_dirs_p - 1:0] scheduled_n;
	wire [input_dirs_p - 1:0] grants_lo;
	bsg_dff_reset #(.width_p(input_dirs_p)) scheduled_reg(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.data_i(scheduled_n),
		.data_o(scheduled_r)
	);
	assign scheduled_with_release = scheduled_r & ~release_i;
	wire free_to_schedule = !scheduled_with_release;
	bsg_round_robin_arb #(.inputs_p(input_dirs_p)) brr(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.grants_en_i(free_to_schedule),
		.reqs_i(reqs_i),
		.grants_o(grants_lo),
		.sel_one_hot_o(),
		.v_o(),
		.tag_o(),
		.yumi_i(free_to_schedule & valid_o)
	);
	assign scheduled_n = grants_lo | scheduled_with_release;
	assign data_sel_o = scheduled_n;
	assign valid_o = ready_i & |(scheduled_n & valid_i);
	assign yumi_o = (ready_i ? scheduled_n & valid_i : 1'sb0);
endmodule
module bsg_lfsr (
	clk,
	reset_i,
	yumi_i,
	o
);
	parameter width_p = -1;
	parameter init_val_p = 1;
	parameter xor_mask_p = 0;
	input clk;
	input reset_i;
	input yumi_i;
	output wire [width_p - 1:0] o;
	reg [width_p - 1:0] o_r;
	wire [width_p - 1:0] o_n;
	wire [width_p - 1:0] xor_mask;
	assign o = o_r;
	generate
		if (xor_mask_p == 0) begin : automask
			case (width_p)
				32: assign xor_mask = (((1 << 31) | (1 << 29)) | (1 << 26)) | (1 << 25);
				60: assign xor_mask = (1 << 59) | (1 << 58);
				64: assign xor_mask = (((1 << 63) | (1 << 62)) | (1 << 60)) | (1 << 59);
				default: initial ;
			endcase
		end
		else begin : fi
			assign xor_mask = xor_mask_p;
		end
	endgenerate
	always @(posedge clk)
		if (reset_i)
			o_r <= sv2v_cast_89401(init_val_p);
		else if (yumi_i)
			o_r <= o_n;
	assign o_n = (o_r >> 1) ^ ({width_p {o_r[0]}} & xor_mask);
	function automatic [width_p - 1:0] sv2v_cast_89401;
		input reg [width_p - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_89401 = inp;
	endfunction
endmodule
module bp_addr_map (
	mmio_cord_i,
	dram_cord_i,
	host_cord_i,
	paddr_i,
	dst_cord_o,
	dst_cid_o
);
	localparam bp_log_none_gp = 0;
	localparam bp_log_stdout_gp = 1;
	localparam bp_log_file_gp = 2;
	localparam bp_eaddr_width_gp = 64;
	localparam bp_instr_width_gp = 32;
	parameter bp_sv39_page_table_depth_gp = 3;
	parameter bp_sv39_pte_width_gp = 64;
	parameter bp_sv39_vaddr_width_gp = 39;
	parameter bp_sv39_paddr_width_gp = 56;
	parameter bp_sv39_ppn_width_gp = 44;
	parameter bp_page_size_in_bytes_gp = 4096;
	parameter bp_page_offset_width_gp = (bp_page_size_in_bytes_gp == 1 ? 1 : $clog2(bp_page_size_in_bytes_gp));
	parameter bp_data_resp_num_flit_gp = 4;
	parameter bp_data_cmd_num_flit_gp = 4;

((((cce_mem_msg_width_lp - 1) >= 0 ? cce_mem_msg_width_lp : 2 - cce_mem_msg_width_lp) + ((mem_noc_cid_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cid_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cid_width_p)) + ((mem_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cord_width_p)) + ((mem_noc_reserved_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_reserved_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_reserved_width_p) : 2 - (((((cce_mem_msg_width_lp - 1) >= 0 ? cce_mem_msg_width_lp : 2 - cce_mem_msg_width_lp) + ((mem_noc_cid_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cid_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cid_width_p)) + ((mem_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cord_width_p)) + ((mem_noc_reserved_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_reserved_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_reserved_width_p))) : 2 - (((((((cce_mem_msg_width_lp - 1) >= 0 ? cce_mem_msg_width_lp : 2 - cce_mem_msg_width_lp) + ((mem_noc_cid_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cid_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cid_width_p)) + ((mem_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cord_width_p)) + ((mem_noc_reserved_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_reserved_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_reserved_width_p)) - 1) >= 0 ? ((((cce_mem_msg_width_lp - 1) >= 0 ? cce_mem_msg_width_lp : 2 - cce_mem_msg_width_lp) + ((mem_noc_cid_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cid_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cid_width_p)) + ((mem_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cord_width_p)) + ((mem_noc_reserved_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_reserved_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_reserved_width_p) : 2 - (((((cce_mem_msg_width_lp - 1) >= 0 ? cce_mem_msg_width_lp : 2 - cce_mem_msg_width_lp) + ((mem_noc_cid_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cid_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cid_width_p)) + ((mem_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cord_width_p)) + ((mem_noc_reserved_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_reserved_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_reserved_width_p)))) + ((mem_noc_cid_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cid_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cid_width_p)) + ((mem_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_len_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_len_width_p)) + ((mem_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cord_width_p)) - 1:0] mem_resp_packet_lo;
	bp_me_wormhole_packet_encode_mem_resp #(.cfg_p(cfg_p)) mem_resp_encode(
		.mem_resp_i(mem_resp_i),
		.src_cord_i(my_cord_i),
		.src_cid_i(my_cid_i),
		.dst_cord_i(dst_cord_lo),
		.dst_cid_i(dst_cid_lo),
		.packet_o(mem_resp_packet_lo)
	);
	bsg_wormhole_router_adapter_in #(
		.max_payload_width_p((((((((cce_mem_msg_width_lp - 1) >= 0 ? cce_mem_msg_width_lp : 2 - cce_mem_msg_width_lp) + ((mem_noc_cid_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cid_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cid_width_p)) + ((mem_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cord_width_p)) + ((mem_noc_reserved_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_reserved_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_reserved_width_p)) - 1) >= 0 ? ((((cce_mem_msg_width_lp - 1) >= 0 ? cce_mem_msg_width_lp : 2 - cce_mem_msg_width_lp) + ((mem_noc_cid_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cid_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cid_width_p)) + ((mem_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cord_width_p)) + ((mem_noc_reserved_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_reserved_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_reserved_width_p) : 2 - (((((cce_mem_msg_width_lp - 1) >= 0 ? cce_mem_msg_width_lp : 2 - cce_mem_msg_width_lp) + ((mem_noc_cid_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cid_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cid_width_p)) + ((mem_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cord_width_p)) + ((mem_noc_reserved_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_reserved_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_reserved_width_p))) + mem_noc_cid_width_p),
		.len_width_p(mem_noc_len_width_p),
		.cord_width_p(mem_noc_cord_width_p),
		.flit_width_p(mem_noc_flit_width_p)
	) mem_resp_adapter_in(
		.clk_i(clk_i),
		.reset_i(reset_i),
		.packet_i(mem_resp_packet_lo),
		.v_i(mem_resp_v_i),
		.ready_o(mem_resp_ready_o),
		.link_i(resp_link_i),
		.link_o(resp_link_o)
	);
endmodule

			e_lce_cmd_sync, e_lce_cmd_set_clear, e_lce_cmd_transfer, e_lce_cmd_writeback, e_lce_cmd_set_tag, e_lce_cmd_set_tag_wakeup, e_lce_cmd_invalidate_tag, e_lce_cmd_uc_st_done: packet_cast_o[((coh_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_len_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_len_width_p) + (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) + -1)-:((((coh_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_len_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_len_width_p) + (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) + -1)) >= ((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) ? ((((coh_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_len_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_len_width_p) + (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) + -1)) - ((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p)) + 1 : (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) - (((coh_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_len_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_len_width_p) + (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) + -1))) + 1)] = sv2v_cast_443F3(lce_cmd_cmd_len_lp);
			e_lce_cmd_data: packet_cast_o[((coh_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_len_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_len_width_p) + (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) + -1)-:((((coh_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_len_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_len_width_p) + (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) + -1)) >= ((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) ? ((((coh_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_len_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_len_width_p) + (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) + -1)) - ((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p)) + 1 : (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) - (((coh_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_len_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_len_width_p) + (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) + -1))) + 1)] = sv2v_cast_443F3(lce_cmd_data_len_lp);
			e_lce_cmd_uc_data: packet_cast_o[((coh_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_len_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_len_width_p) + (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) + -1)-:((((coh_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_len_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_len_width_p) + (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) + -1)) >= ((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) ? ((((coh_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_len_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_len_width_p) + (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) + -1)) - ((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p)) + 1 : (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) - (((coh_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_len_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_len_width_p) + (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) + -1))) + 1)] = sv2v_cast_443F3(lce_cmd_uc_data_len_lp);
			default: packet_cast_o = 1'sb0;
		endcase
	end
	function automatic [all_cfgs_gp[cfg_p].coh_noc_len_width - 1:0] sv2v_cast_443F3;
		input reg [all_cfgs_gp[cfg_p].coh_noc_len_width - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_443F3 = inp;
	endfunction
endmodule

((((coh_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_len_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_len_width_p) + (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) + -1)) - ((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p)) + 1 : (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) - (((coh_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_len_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_len_width_p) + (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) + -1))) + 1)] = sv2v_cast_443F3(lce_cce_resp_wb_len_lp);
			e_lce_cce_resp_null_wb: packet_cast_o[((coh_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_len_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_len_width_p) + (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) + -1)-:((((coh_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_len_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_len_width_p) + (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) + -1)) >= ((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) ? ((((coh_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_len_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_len_width_p) + (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) + -1)) - ((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p)) + 1 : (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) - (((coh_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_len_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_len_width_p) + (((coh_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? coh_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - coh_noc_cord_width_p) + -1))) + 1)] = sv2v_cast_443F3(lce_cce_resp_ack_len_lp);
			default: packet_cast_o = 1'sb0;
		endcase
	end
	function automatic [all_cfgs_gp[cfg_p].coh_noc_len_width - 1:0] sv2v_cast_443F3;
		input reg [all_cfgs_gp[cfg_p].coh_noc_len_width - 1:0] inp;
		sv2v_cast_443F3 = inp;
	endfunction
endmodule

		packet_cast_o[((mem_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cord_width_p) + -1-:((((mem_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cord_width_p) + -1) >= 0 ? 		case (mem_cmd_cast_i[3 + (((paddr_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? paddr_width_p : 2 - paddr_width_p) + 3)-:((3 + (((paddr_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? paddr_width_p : 2 - paddr_width_p) + 3)) >= (((paddr_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? paddr_width_p : 2 - paddr_width_p) + 4) ? ((3 + (((paddr_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? paddr_width_p : 2 - paddr_width_p) + 3)) - (((paddr_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? paddr_width_p : 2 - paddr_width_p) + 4)) + 1 : ((((paddr_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? paddr_width_p : 2 - paddr_width_p) + 4) - (3 + (((paddr_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? paddr_width_p : 2 - paddr_width_p) + 3))) + 1)])

((((mem_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_len_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_len_width_p) + (((mem_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cord_width_p) + -1)) - ((mem_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cord_width_p)) + 1 : (((mem_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cord_width_p) - (((mem_noc_len_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_len_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_len_width_p) + (((mem_noc_cord_width_p - 1) >= 0 ? mem_noc_cord_width_p : 2 - mem_noc_cord_width_p) + -1))) + 1)] = sv2v_cast_79A6F(mem_cmd_req_len_lp);

			default: packet_cast_o = 1'sb0;
		endcase
	end
	function automatic [all_cfgs_gp[cfg_p].mem_noc_len_width - 1:0] sv2v_cast_79A6F;
